---
import GitHubIcon from '../assets/github.svg';
import Layout from '../layouts/General.astro';
---

<Layout title='About Me' description='about me, jsmz profile, contact information'>
  <div class='container'>
  <section class='profile'>
    <img src='/img/me.webp' alt='jsmz profile' width='128' height='128' />
    <div class='info'>
      <h1>jsmz</h1>
      <ul class='meta'>
        <li>🖳 都内の Web 系企業で SRE やってます</li>
        <li>🕮 修士(工学)</li>
        <li>
          <span class='heart'>❤</span>
          Container, 公開鍵暗号, HTTP, アプリケーションセキュリティ, Web, Public Cloud, SRE, Emacs
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class='links'>
        <span>✉ contact(あっと)blog.jsmz.dev</span>
        <a href='https://github.com/jjjsmz' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>
          <GitHubIcon aria-hidden='true' />@jjjsmz
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <p class='note'>
    本 blog のソースコードは GitHub 上で公開しています．<br />
    誤字脱字や内容の誤りなどがあれば <a
      href='https://github.com/jjjsmz/blog/issues/new'
      target='_blank'
      rel='noopener noreferrer'>Issue</a
    > よりご指摘いただけますと幸いです．
  </p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .profile {
    margin-top: 4em;
    margin-bottom: 3em;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2em;
    align-items: flex-start;

    @media (width <= 480px) {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }

  img {
    border-radius: 50%;
    min-width: 128px;
  }

  .info {
    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 0.75em;
      font-size: 1.4em;
      color: var(--text-bright);
    }

    .meta {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0 0 1em;

      li {
        margin: 0.3em 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        gap: 0.4em;
      }
    }
  }

  .heart {
    color: #ffa0a0;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4em;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);

    a {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4em;

      svg {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        fill: currentColor;
      }
    }
  }

  .note {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--bg-secondary);
    padding-top: 2em;
  }
</style>
